text: Ion Coliban (born 6 June 1925) was a Romanian alpine skier. He competed at the 1948 Winter Olympics and the 1952 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Romanian male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Romania Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:Alpine skiers at the 1952 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Brașov
